The order in which the scripts must be executed is:

**1) drifting_gratings.py # Makes the simulation of the network and stores the data
**2) network_topology.py # Analyzes the structural connectivity of the network
*_2) neurons_dynamic_classification.py # Obtains the variables variations and dynamically classifies neurons
*_3) dynamic_populations_comparison.py # Represents the average of a certain magnitude (e.g. input current) for different neuronal populations
*_3) neurons_dynamic_analysis.py # Analyze the dynamic synaptic weights of the neurons types
*_3) synapses_analysis.py # Analyze the structural characteristics of dVf, hVf and unc neurons
*_3) stimulus_classification_comparison.py # Compare how the dynamic classification changes with different stimulus
*_3) feature_selectivity_analysis.py # Analyze the orientation and frequency effect on the classification
*_3) classes_spatial_distribution_analysis.py # Analyze the K ripley function and radius and height distribution of the neurons from the different classes
**4) full_field_flash.py
*-4) perturbation_responsive_neurons_analysis.py
